OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Quickie' divorces and will
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwriting to be probed       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Firms offering "quickie" divorces and  
OL,6, will writing are to be investigated by 
OL,7, the UK's competition watchdog.         
OL,9,FThe Competition and Markets Authority  
OL,10,F(CMA) said it would examine claims made
OL,11,Fby online divorce services, which have 
OL,12,Fbecome more popular since lockdown.    
OL,14,FSome vulnerable customers had also     
OL,15,Fcontacted it after being pressured into
OL,16,Fsigning up for will-writing services.  
OL,18,FThe CMA said there were now many       
OL,19,Falternatives to law firms, especially  
OL,20,Fwhere the adviser is not a solicitor.  
